---
title: Grilled Chicken Summer Salad with Strawberry Vinaigrette
description: Get ready for a summer winner! Briny feta, sweet strawberry and crunchy walnuts form the perfect trio in this summer salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-estivale-de-poulet-grille-f32733cd.jpg
